message: Changes to the infobox. Hungary and Romania removed from the Axis side, as their involvement in the Mediterranean theatre is negligible. Croatia made an Italian puppet state as it was only nominally independent (being occupied by the Axis) and had an Italian member of the House of Savoy as its monarch. Ethiopian troops also fought in this theatre after its liberation in 1941. The Italian social republic was also placed under Germany as it was a mere puppet state without independence like Croatia
